<P ID="6"><ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Estrada</ENAMEX> is a senior at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Compass High School</ENAMEX>. He was nominated for the award by <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Crystal Felman</ENAMEX>, a counselor at the school. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Felman</ENAMEX> said <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Estrada</ENAMEX> maintains a positive attitude and is honest, noting that he found a money order written for a large sum of money in the Westside Market parking lot and turned the money order into the staff at the school.
