<P ID="22"><ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">City</ENAMEX> Clerk <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Anita Posse</ENAMEX> noted that after the resolution was originally approved she inadvertently inputted the wrong rate schedule into the computer. The amendment corrects the rate change.
